Module	Runs In	Purpose	Isolation Level	Persistence
Enclave	Secure Enclave	Key gen, rotation, wake-word inference	Highest (hw)	Yes
Sandbox	App container	Voice processing, command parsing, UI	Medium	Yes
Listener	Sandbox	Always-on mic stream → Enclave	Medium	Yes
ara_replace.py	User space	One-time bootstrap, perm grants, logging	Low	No
TZNG Auditor	Sandbox	Log encryption, drift detection, export	Medium	Yes
GUI Dashboard	Sandbox	Live status, start/stop, log tail	Low	No
